01:59.353 --> 02:00.654
♪♪ IT'S THE TIME TO SHOUT ♪♪

02:00.687 --> 02:02.689
♪♪ SO WE GATHER AROUND
TO ENTICE THE CROWD ♪♪

02:02.723 --> 02:05.626
♪♪ PICK THE ENERGY UP
AND THEN PASS IT AROUND ♪♪

02:05.659 --> 02:06.860
♪♪ DO IT ♪♪

02:06.894 --> 02:08.428
♪♪ EVERYBODY FEELING GOOD
LIKE I THINK THEY SHOULD ♪♪

02:08.462 --> 02:10.998
♪♪ MAKE 'EM MOVE, MAKE 'EM ALL
SAY THE SONG IS GOOD ♪♪

02:11.031 --> 02:12.633
♪♪ IT'S ALL RIGHT NOW ♪♪

02:12.666 --> 02:13.800
♪♪ IT'S ALL GOOD ♪♪

02:13.834 --> 02:15.469
WHOA! YO!

02:15.502 --> 02:16.603
YO!

02:17.137 --> 02:20.774
YO, WHAT'S UP, MAN?

02:20.807 --> 02:22.576
I'M GOOD, MAN.

02:22.609 --> 02:24.278
HEY, MAN.

02:24.311 --> 02:26.380
YOU BRING ME
A TALL, CREAMY PRESENT?

02:26.413 --> 02:29.049
DUDE, THE CREAM PUFF'S
GOT TWO KIDS AND A NEW HUSBAND.

02:29.082 --> 02:31.618
I BROUGHT YOU SOMETHING BETTER.
CHECK THIS OUT.

02:31.652 --> 02:32.786
EXCUSE ME.

02:32.819 --> 02:34.922
MY NAME IS VERNON.
I'M A SCORPIO.

02:34.955 --> 02:37.124
LACY ‐‐ ME TOO.

02:37.157 --> 02:39.393
I'D LIKE TO GET YOU HIGH.
ALL RIGHT.

02:39.426 --> 02:41.929
BECAUSE CONRAD AND I
HAVE COME UP WITH A NEW STRAIN,

02:41.962 --> 02:43.430
AND WE'RE REALLY PROUD OF IT.

02:43.463 --> 02:45.832
ACTUALLY, I'D LIKE A SNACK
OUT OF THAT VAC‐PACK

02:45.866 --> 02:47.000
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

02:47.034 --> 02:48.735
IT'S NOT THAT
I DON'T TRUST YOU.

02:48.769 --> 02:50.270
IT'S JUST
I DON'T TRUST CONRAD.

02:50.304 --> 02:52.272
NOW YOU TRYING
TO HURT MY FEELINGS, VERNON.

02:52.306 --> 02:55.042
ONLY SHE CAN CALL ME VERNON.
YOU CALL ME "SIR."

02:55.075 --> 02:57.945
YOU GOT A BONG
UP IN HERE, MAN?

02:57.978 --> 02:59.546
LOAD IT UP.
LOAD IT UP.

03:00.581 --> 03:02.282
THAT'S YOU.
YOU LIT?

03:02.316 --> 03:04.318
ALL RIGHT,
LET'S SEE WHAT YOU GOT.

03:04.351 --> 03:06.653
[ BUBBLING ]

03:10.858 --> 03:12.826
WHAT DO YOU THINK, VERNON?

03:12.860 --> 03:13.961
YOU RESPONSIBLE FOR THIS?

03:13.994 --> 03:17.564
YEAH ‐‐ US.
CONRAD MOSTLY.

03:17.598 --> 03:18.966
IT'S GOOD, ISN'T?

03:18.999 --> 03:20.234
IT'S SMOKALICIOUS.

03:20.267 --> 03:21.935
WHAT UP, MY NIG?
WHAT TO DO, NEPHEW?

03:21.969 --> 03:23.370
Vernon:
HEY, MAN, CHECK THIS OUT.

03:23.403 --> 03:26.740
MY MAN CONRAD PIMPING SOME
NEW PRODUCT. FAN‐TIZZLE‐TASTIC.

03:26.773 --> 03:28.442
YOU LIKE THAT THERE.

03:28.475 --> 03:29.443
HEY, LOOK HERE.

03:29.476 --> 03:31.945
I WANT TO INTRODUCE YOU
TO THE LOVELY LACY,

03:31.979 --> 03:34.414
HIS PARTNER IN CRIME
AND A VERY MARRIED MILF.

03:34.448 --> 03:36.016
AND THAT'S JUST
BREAKING MY HEART.

03:36.049 --> 03:38.452
IS THAT RIGHT?

03:38.485 --> 03:41.154
I'D DEFINITELY DO YOU.
OH, GEE, THANKS.

03:41.188 --> 03:43.557
MY NAME'S SNOOP DOGG,
BABY.

03:43.590 --> 03:44.424
LACY. HI.

03:44.458 --> 03:46.393
THAT'S THAT MOTHER‐FUCKING
MILF WEED.

03:46.426 --> 03:48.695
YOU KNOW WHAT THE MILF WEED IS,
RIGHT, MY NIGGA?

03:48.729 --> 03:51.164
MOTHER I'D
LOVE TO FUCK.
MOTHER I'D
LOVE TO FUCK.

03:51.198 --> 03:52.533
FOR SURE, THAT'S THAT MILF WEED.

03:52.566 --> 03:55.602
♪♪ MAKE A NIGGA TAKE A TOKE,
IT'S THE MILF WEED ♪♪

03:55.636 --> 03:58.438
♪♪ MAKE A NIGGA HAVE A SMOKE,
IT'S THE MILF WEED ♪♪

03:58.472 --> 04:00.207
TAKE THAT INTO THE BOOTH
AND PUT IT DOWN.

04:00.240 --> 04:02.409
FOR SURE.
LET'S GO DO IT.

04:02.442 --> 04:05.679
PUMP THE MUSIC UP WHILE I TALK
ABOUT THIS WEED I JUST BOUGHT.

04:05.712 --> 04:07.114
♪♪ IT'S CALLED THE MILF WEED ♪♪

04:07.147 --> 04:09.416
♪♪ IT'S THE GETTING ON ME SMOKE,
IT'S THE MILF WEED ♪♪

04:09.449 --> 04:11.552
♪♪ TAKE A TOKE TILL YOU'RE BROKE,
IT'S THE MILF WEED ♪♪

04:11.585 --> 04:13.887
♪♪ NIGGA JUST CAN'T QUIT,
IT'S THE MILF WEED ♪♪

04:13.921 --> 04:15.422
♪♪ NIGGA, CAN I GET
ANOTHER HIT? ♪♪

04:15.455 --> 04:18.058
♪♪ IT'S STRONG AND IT'S GREEN
LIKE THE HULK WHEN HE ANGRY ♪♪

04:18.091 --> 04:20.427
♪♪ BREAK IT UP, BREAK IT UP,
SMOKE IT UP TANGY ♪♪

04:20.460 --> 04:22.429
♪♪ TASTING THE WAY YOU FEEL,
THE WAY THAT IT SMELL ♪♪

04:22.462 --> 04:25.098
♪♪ THE WAY IT MAKE A NIGGA FEEL,
OH, SO WELL ♪♪

04:25.132 --> 04:26.600
♪♪ I'M‐A TELL IT TO YOU, TO YOU ♪♪

04:26.633 --> 04:27.668
♪♪ SO YOU NEED TO KNOW ♪♪

04:27.701 --> 04:29.870
♪♪ WE SMOKING MILF WEED EVERY DAY
ON THE ROAD ♪♪

04:29.903 --> 04:32.406
♪♪ WE GET IT CRACKING‐LIKE,
AND EVERY TIME YOU SEE ME, DOG ♪♪

04:32.439 --> 04:34.708
♪♪ IT'S SNOOP D‐O DOUBLE "G"
BLAZE THE END OUT ♪♪

04:34.741 --> 04:37.344
♪♪ WE GOT THE MILF 'CAUSE
THE MILF GOT IT ALL THE TIME ♪♪

04:37.377 --> 04:39.947
♪♪ GOT THE WEED THAT BE
MAKIN' NIGGA BLOW HIS MIND ♪♪

04:39.980 --> 04:42.149
♪♪ IT'S THE WEED THAT FEEL GOOD,
SMELL GOOD ♪♪

04:42.182 --> 04:44.551
♪♪ IT'S THE WEED
THAT YOU CAN'T GET IN THE HOOD ♪♪

04:44.585 --> 04:46.887
♪♪ YOU GOT TO HAVE A CONNECT
ON THE SET ♪♪

04:46.920 --> 04:48.288
♪♪ LET ME GET SOME OF THAT SHIT ♪♪

04:48.322 --> 04:49.623
♪♪ MAKE IT FAST, JET ♪♪

04:49.656 --> 04:50.557
♪♪ GIVE IT TO ME QUICK ♪♪

04:50.591 --> 04:52.159
♪♪ GIVE IT TO ME FAST ♪♪

04:52.192 --> 04:53.760
♪♪ I WANNA TAP YOU
ON YOUR WHITE ASS ♪♪

04:53.794 --> 04:56.630
♪♪ 'CAUSE YOU'S THE MOTHER
THAT I'D LOVE TO FUCK ♪♪

04:56.663 --> 04:57.831
YOU DONE GOOD, KIDS.

04:57.865 --> 05:00.901
MAYBE YOU COME BY TOMORROW
AND BRING US A LITTLE MORE LOVE,

05:00.934 --> 05:05.439
SAY, TWO OR THREE
OF THOSE HAPPY PACKS.

05:05.472 --> 05:07.741
ABSOLUTELY, VERN.

05:07.774 --> 05:09.176
GET THE HELL
OUT OF HERE, MAN.

05:09.209 --> 05:11.578
THIS IS A PLACE OF BUSINESS,
AND I GOT WORK TO DO.

05:11.612 --> 05:12.579
YOU'RE A BAD INFLUENCE.

05:12.613 --> 05:15.549
OH, OH, OH.
IT WAS NICE MEETING YOU, LACY.

05:15.582 --> 05:16.683
PLEASURE, VERNON.

05:18.151 --> 05:20.888
MILF WEED?
MILF WEED?!

05:20.921 --> 05:22.789
THIS SHIT
IS ABOUT TO GET WILD.

05:22.823 --> 05:24.958
FANTASTIC!

05:24.992 --> 05:27.194
FOR REAL!
LET'S GO MAKE SOME MONEY!

05:29.162 --> 05:30.998
YOU GET A NEW WIG?

05:31.031 --> 05:34.768
NOPE.
IT'S MINE ‐‐ SORT OF.

05:34.801 --> 05:36.403
I'M WEARING 500 BUCKS WORTH

05:36.436 --> 05:39.406
OF HUMAN HAIR EXTENSIONS
FROM INDIA.

05:39.439 --> 05:40.440
TAKE A SNIFF.

05:40.474 --> 05:43.343
THERE'S A FAINT CURRY SMELL
TO IT.

05:43.377 --> 05:47.514
I'M GIVING AN ANTI‐DRUG SPEECH
AT THE GRAMMAR SCHOOL,

05:47.548 --> 05:50.984
AND I NEED YOU TO BE SOBER.

05:51.018 --> 05:52.286
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT?

05:52.319 --> 05:55.989
SOBER THE SASQUATCH.
HE TELLS KIDS TO STAY OFF DRUGS.

05:56.023 --> 05:57.558
AND YOU THINK KIDS
ARE GONNA LISTEN

05:57.591 --> 06:00.027
BECAUSE SOME IDIOT'S
DRESSED IN A GORILLA SUIT?

06:00.060 --> 06:02.296
NO, IT'S A SASQUATCH.

06:02.329 --> 06:05.465
CHILDREN LOVE AND FEAR HIM.

06:05.499 --> 06:06.366
THAT'S ASININE.

06:06.400 --> 06:08.368
OH, COME ON, DEAN.
YOU'RE PERFECT FOR IT.

06:08.402 --> 06:10.170
AND IF I STOP
SHAVING YOUR BACK,

06:10.204 --> 06:12.139
YOU WON'T EVEN
HAVE TO WEAR THE SUIT.

06:12.172 --> 06:13.440
AND NOW I WALK AWAY.

06:13.473 --> 06:16.343
HEY, BUT GOOD LUCK
WITH THAT SPEECH,

06:16.376 --> 06:20.047
BECAUSE KIDS JUST LOVE
BEING PATRONIZED AND LECTURED.

06:20.080 --> 06:21.148
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

06:21.181 --> 06:23.483
I HEAR YOU WANT
TO CLOSE THE PARK.

06:23.517 --> 06:26.220
WHERE AM I SUPPOSED TO TAKE
MY BABIES?

06:26.253 --> 06:27.187
WHAT?

06:27.221 --> 06:29.523
WHERE ARE MY BABIES
SUPPOSED TO PLAY?

06:29.556 --> 06:31.358
OH, YOU MEAN YOUR DOGS.

06:31.391 --> 06:34.862
THEY'RE MY CHILDREN.
THEY NEED THEIR PARK.

06:34.895 --> 06:37.998
NO, REAL CHILDREN
NEED THEIR PARK.

06:38.031 --> 06:40.234
DOGS NEED TO TAKE A WALK,

06:40.267 --> 06:42.236
DO THEIR BUSINESS,
AND THEN GO HOME.

06:42.269 --> 06:45.372
BUT THE DOG PARK IS GATED OFF.
THE DOGS DON'T BOTHER ANYONE.

06:45.405 --> 06:47.374
THAT WHOLE PLACE
STINKS TO HIGH HEAVEN.

06:47.407 --> 06:50.043
IT'S AN EYESORE FROM ALL
THE GRASS THAT'S BEEN DUG UP.

06:50.077 --> 06:53.413
THERE'S BARKING AND SNARLING
GOING ON ALL DAY LONG.

06:53.447 --> 06:56.450
AND AT NIGHT,
WHEN THE DOGS FINALLY LEAVE,

06:56.483 --> 06:59.987
IT'S FILLED WITH TEENAGERS
DOING DRUGS.

07:00.020 --> 07:04.057
IT IS A BLIGHT ON THIS
COMMUNITY, AND IT'S GOING.

07:04.091 --> 07:07.661
DO YOU KNOW WHAT YOU ARE?
YOU ARE A HATER.

07:07.694 --> 07:09.296
YOU'RE FILLED WITH HATE,

07:09.329 --> 07:12.366
AND YOU SPREAD IT AROUND
TO DOGS AND TEENAGERS ‐‐

07:12.399 --> 07:16.303
AND YOU, BECAUSE
YOU CALL YOUR PETS CHILDREN.

07:16.336 --> 07:17.471
SO GOODBYE.

07:17.504 --> 07:19.273
[ DOGS WHIMPERING ]

07:19.306 --> 07:22.643
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

07:22.676 --> 07:24.912
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

07:24.945 --> 07:27.247
Dean: DAMN IT!

07:27.281 --> 07:28.615
PAYDAY!

07:28.649 --> 07:31.251
I'M HERE.
I'M RIGHT HERE.

07:31.285 --> 07:33.487
SANJAY.

07:35.489 --> 07:36.390
WOW.

07:36.423 --> 07:37.658
WE THREW IN
A LITTLE BONUS.

07:37.691 --> 07:40.827
FOR THE ARSON ‐‐ NOT TO BE TAKEN
AS ENCOURAGEMENT.

07:40.861 --> 07:42.262
NEVER AGAIN, OKAY?

07:42.296 --> 07:43.630
OKAY.

07:43.664 --> 07:45.432
DEAN.

07:45.465 --> 07:49.269
NICE ‐‐
NO I. R. S. AND NO CELIA.

07:49.303 --> 07:51.538
PEOPLE SEEM TO LIKE
WHAT WE'RE SELLING.

07:51.572 --> 07:52.573
DOUG.

07:52.606 --> 07:53.807
SWEET.

07:53.841 --> 07:55.876
FIRST TIME SOMEBODY'S
PAID ME FOR WEED.

07:55.909 --> 07:58.779
BUY A MOTORCYCLE.
WE CAN RIDE TOGETHER.

07:58.812 --> 08:00.147
YOU'RE DEAD TO ME.

08:00.180 --> 08:02.349
I'M OUT OF HERE.
EXCUSE ME.

08:02.382 --> 08:03.984
WHAT?

08:04.017 --> 08:05.719
UH, YOU FORGOT SOMETHING.

08:05.752 --> 08:07.855
NO, I DIDN'T.

08:07.888 --> 08:09.990
UH, YEAH, YOU DID ‐‐
MY ENVELOPE.

08:10.023 --> 08:11.658
OH, YOU DON'T GET ONE.

08:11.692 --> 08:13.660
I DON'T ‐‐

08:13.694 --> 08:16.496
WAIT A SECOND.
I DON'T GET PAID?

08:16.530 --> 08:19.967
ONCE YOU REIMBURSE ME
FOR ROOM AND BOARD

08:20.000 --> 08:23.570
AND FOR A NONREFUNDABLE YEAR
OF RABBINICAL SCHOOL

08:23.604 --> 08:26.640
AND FOR THE TIME I BAILED
YOU OUT WHEN YOU GOT BUSTED,

08:26.673 --> 08:28.041
NOT TO MENTION
LAWYERS' FEES,

08:28.075 --> 08:30.277
THEN YOU'LL BE COMPENSATED,
YEAH.

08:32.312 --> 08:37.050
ARE YOU JOKING?
I LOST TOES FOR YOU.

08:37.084 --> 08:38.352
I WAS IN A RAID.

08:38.385 --> 08:40.187
I SAT IN MY OWN PEE
TO SAVE THE MOTHER.

08:40.220 --> 08:42.689
BACK ME UP HERE, GUYS.

08:52.165 --> 08:54.635
I'M A CONTRIBUTING MEMBER
OF THIS TEAM.

08:56.403 --> 08:57.437
I COOK!

09:00.674 --> 09:01.742
IS THAT HOW IT IS?

09:03.477 --> 09:06.547
ALL RIGHT, THAT'S FINE.
WELL, I QUIT.

09:13.053 --> 09:14.288
[ LAUGHTER ]

09:14.321 --> 09:16.223
Conrad: COOK LIKE
A FUCKING CRACKHEAD.

09:16.256 --> 09:19.593
HE COOKS.
HE COOKS.

09:21.595 --> 09:22.696
SETTLE, BOYS AND GIRLS.

09:22.729 --> 09:25.666
LET'S ALL PUT ON OUR LISTENING
EARS AND SETTLE DOWN.

09:25.699 --> 09:27.034
THAT'S BETTER.

09:27.067 --> 09:29.736
NOW, I'D LIKE TO WELCOME TODAY'S
SPECIAL GUEST SPEAKER,

09:29.770 --> 09:31.638
COUNCILWOMAN HODES.

09:31.672 --> 09:35.242
[ LIGHT APPLAUSE ]

09:35.275 --> 09:38.745
WELL, HELLO,
JUNIOR CITIZENS OF AGRESTIC.

09:38.779 --> 09:41.648
I AM COUNCILWOMAN HODES,

09:41.682 --> 09:46.587
AND I AM HERE TODAY AT OUR
TOP‐RANKED GRAMMAR SCHOOL...

09:49.489 --> 09:52.059
...TO MAKE A VERY SPECIAL
ANNOUNCEMENT.

09:52.092 --> 09:53.460
BEGINNING NEXT WEEK,

09:53.493 --> 09:58.532
ALL OF AGRESTIC WILL BECOME
A DRUG‐FREE ZONE.

10:04.505 --> 10:06.240
OKAY...

10:06.273 --> 10:11.278
YOU KNOW HOW PENGUINS
MARCH 70 MILES

10:11.311 --> 10:13.580
TO GET WHERE THEY'RE GOING?

10:13.614 --> 10:16.350
WELL, DRUGS ARE LIKE PENGUINS.

10:16.383 --> 10:21.188
THEY MARCH FROM THE GHETTO
TO THE SUBURBS.

10:21.221 --> 10:23.257
NOW, TO END THIS MIGRATION,

10:23.290 --> 10:26.360
I WILL BE INSTALLING
SURVEILLANCE CAMERAS

10:26.393 --> 10:31.131
AND "DRUG FREE ZONE" SIGNS
THROUGHOUT AGRESTIC.

10:31.164 --> 10:32.599
I INVITE YOU
TO BRING YOUR PARENTS

10:32.633 --> 10:35.435
TO THE UNVEILING
OF OUR FIRST SURVEILLANCE CAMERA

10:35.469 --> 10:39.373
TOMORROW AT THE CORNER
OF HILLSIDE AND HARPER DRIVES,

10:39.406 --> 10:42.709
RIGHT ACROSS FROM WHAT WILL SOON
NO LONGER BE THE DOG PARK.

10:42.743 --> 10:44.211
4:00 P. M.

10:44.244 --> 10:48.282
AND NOW I WOULD LIKE TO
INTRODUCE A VERY SPECIAL GUEST

10:48.315 --> 10:51.418
WHO HAS AN IMPORTANT MESSAGE
FOR YOU ALL ‐‐

10:51.451 --> 10:54.254
SOBER THE SASQUATCH!

10:55.722 --> 10:56.690
[ ROARS ]

10:56.723 --> 10:58.392
[ LAUGHTER ]

10:58.425 --> 11:02.262
DRUGS ARE WRONG!

11:03.597 --> 11:04.765
[ GROWLING ]

11:04.798 --> 11:10.270
I'M PUTTING MY BIG FOOT
DOWN ON DRUGS!

11:10.304 --> 11:12.272
MY BIG FOOT!

11:12.306 --> 11:14.608
THIS IS NOT A GAME, PEOPLE.

11:16.476 --> 11:18.278
YES, SHANE?

11:18.312 --> 11:20.814
POINT OF ORDER ‐‐
WHY CAMERAS?

11:20.848 --> 11:21.982
GOOD QUESTION.

11:22.015 --> 11:25.419
BECAUSE
PEOPLE BEHAVE BETTER

11:25.452 --> 11:27.988
WHEN THEY KNOW
THEY'RE BEING WATCHED.

11:28.021 --> 11:31.325
WHAT ABOUT
OUR RIGHTS TO PRIVACY?

11:31.358 --> 11:33.827
WELL, THERE ARE
MORE IMPORTANT THINGS

11:33.861 --> 11:35.596
THAN RIGHTS TO PRIVACY.

11:35.629 --> 11:36.697
AND NOW ‐‐

11:36.730 --> 11:39.633
I THINK YOU'RE TURNING AGRESTIC
INTO A POLICE STATE.

11:39.666 --> 11:41.468
[ CHEERING ]

11:43.036 --> 11:44.605
DRUGS ARE WRONG!

11:44.638 --> 11:47.574
[ CHILDREN BOO ]

11:50.310 --> 11:53.647
I'VE SEEN YOU
DRUNK AT MY HOUSE.

11:55.549 --> 11:57.084
I BEG YOUR PARDON?

11:57.117 --> 11:59.453
NOT LIKE THE DRUNKEN, HOMELESS
PENGUINS IN THE GHETTO,

11:59.486 --> 12:01.421
BUT I'VE DEFINITELY
SEEN YOU DRUNK.

12:01.455 --> 12:03.390
WELL, THAT'S QUITE ENOUGH,
SHANE. YOU CAN SIT DOWN.

12:03.423 --> 12:07.861
ISN'T BEING DRUNK LIKE BEING
ON DRUGS? ISN'T ALCOHOL A DRUG?

12:07.895 --> 12:10.430
YOU DO DRUGS.

12:10.464 --> 12:12.699
YOU DO. YOU DO DRUGS.

12:12.733 --> 12:14.668
DRUGS ARE WRONG!

12:14.701 --> 12:18.005
Children: [ Chanting ]
YOU DO DRUGS! YOU DO DRUGS!

12:18.038 --> 12:20.908
THE COUNCILWOMAN ALSO LIKES
HER SPEED AND AMBIEN.

12:20.941 --> 12:23.343
[ CHANTING CONTINUES ]

12:26.613 --> 12:28.549
CHRIST, LET'S GO.

12:33.253 --> 12:36.190
Man: ALL RIGHT, THAT'S
QUITE ENOUGH. SETTLE DOWN.

12:36.223 --> 12:39.726
WOW, MY SWEAT
SMELLS LIKE PEANUTS.

12:45.032 --> 12:48.335
YOU KICKED ASS.
YOU TOOK HODES OUT.

12:48.368 --> 12:50.537
PROPS TO YOU, YO.

12:50.571 --> 12:54.641
THAT WAS AWESOME,
SHANE.

12:58.111 --> 12:59.646
ARE YOU GUYS...

12:59.680 --> 13:00.681
SHUT UP.

13:00.714 --> 13:02.616
NO WAY.

13:02.649 --> 13:05.953
♪♪ BA BUM BA BUM ♪♪

13:05.986 --> 13:07.621
CAN I SEE THAT ONE, PLEASE?

13:07.654 --> 13:10.624
THAT'S THE DIAMOND BLOSSOM.

13:12.893 --> 13:16.730
YEAH, THE RIGHT‐HAND DIAMOND
IS VERY POPULAR THESE DAYS.

13:16.763 --> 13:18.365
ALL THE STARS
ARE WEARING THEM.

13:18.398 --> 13:21.635
IT'S A SYMBOL OF INDEPENDENCE
AND PERSONAL REWARD.

13:21.668 --> 13:24.738
WELL, I DESERVE A REWARD.

13:24.771 --> 13:26.507
I'VE DONE VERY WELL LATELY.

13:26.540 --> 13:28.675
HOW WELL?

13:30.410 --> 13:33.180
OKAY, TAKE OFF
THAT PIECE OF SHIT.

13:33.213 --> 13:35.682
I'VE GOT JEWELRY
TO SHOW YOU.

13:35.716 --> 13:39.186
♪♪ A LIFE WILL BE REAL SUNNY ♪♪

13:39.219 --> 13:42.089
♪♪ WITH MONEY, MONEY,
MONEY, MONEY, MONEY ♪♪

13:42.122 --> 13:45.325
♪♪ YES, LIFE CAN BE SO SUNNY ♪♪

13:45.359 --> 13:48.262
♪♪ WITH MONEY, MONEY,
MONEY, MONEY, MONEY ♪♪

13:48.295 --> 13:50.831
♪♪ IF HAPPINESS INTENDED
ONLY FOR THE POOR ♪♪

13:50.864 --> 13:53.967
♪♪ WELL, I DON'T THINK THAT
I WANT TO GO THERE ANYMORE ♪♪

13:54.001 --> 13:57.171
♪♪ BECAUSE LIFE CAN BE SO SUNNY ♪♪

13:57.204 --> 13:59.873
♪♪ WITH MONEY, MONEY,
MONEY, MONEY, MONEY ♪♪

13:59.907 --> 14:01.508
NO!

14:01.542 --> 14:03.143
NO.

14:03.177 --> 14:04.678
SHANE, WHAT'S WRONG?

14:04.711 --> 14:06.079
YOU TOTALED MY CAR.

14:06.113 --> 14:10.017
OH, SWEETIE, I'M SORRY.
I DIDN'T SEE IT.

14:10.050 --> 14:12.686
I'M NOT USED TO DRIVING
THIS LOW TO THE GROUND.

14:12.719 --> 14:14.321
DID YOU TOTAL YOUR CAR, TOO?

14:14.354 --> 14:16.390
WHAT?

14:16.423 --> 14:18.659
NO. THE LEASE WAS UP.
I JUST BOUGHT THIS.

14:18.692 --> 14:19.860
ISN'T IT CUTE?

14:19.893 --> 14:22.996
NO, IT'S CRAPPY AND SMALL.

14:23.030 --> 14:24.865
IT'S ENVIRONMENTALLY
RESPONSIBLE.

14:24.898 --> 14:26.166
I LIKED THE RANGE ROVER.

14:26.200 --> 14:30.003
THE RANGE ROVER
WAS OBNOXIOUS.

14:30.037 --> 14:31.438
THERE'S GLOBAL WARMING.

14:31.471 --> 14:35.676
AND UNLESS YOU WANT THE PLANET
TO DISSOLVE TO ONE BIG OCEAN...

14:35.709 --> 14:38.345
GLOBAL WARMING
IS JUST GOD'S WILL.

14:38.378 --> 14:41.281
I LIKED THE RANGE ROVER.
THIS CAR IS GAY.

14:41.315 --> 14:44.384
DON'T BE IGNORANT
JUST BECAUSE IT'S IN RIGHT NOW.

14:44.418 --> 14:46.620
THINK ABOUT THE PLANET
FOR A CHANGE.

14:46.653 --> 14:48.488
WHAT IS ALL THIS STUFF?

14:48.522 --> 14:51.558
MOMMY DECIDED TO BUY HERSELF
A FEW THINGS.

14:51.592 --> 14:52.726
A LOT OF THINGS.

14:52.759 --> 14:54.194
YES, A LOT OF THINGS.

14:54.228 --> 14:56.463
I WORK HARD.
I DESERVE THEM.

14:56.496 --> 14:58.665
WHAT WORK?

15:00.100 --> 15:02.970
I RUN A FAMILY.

15:04.204 --> 15:07.274
DID YOU BUY ME ANYTHING?
NO.

15:07.307 --> 15:09.710
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU DESERVE ANYTHING
AFTER WHAT YOU DID TODAY?

15:09.743 --> 15:10.711
WHAT DID I DO?

15:10.744 --> 15:12.746
YOU CALLED CELIA HODES
A DRUNK.

15:12.779 --> 15:14.214
I GOT ANOTHER CALL

15:14.248 --> 15:17.384
FROM MY DEAR OLD FRIEND
PRINCIPAL DODGE.

15:17.417 --> 15:20.053
I THINK
I'M ON HIS SPEED DIAL.

15:21.622 --> 15:22.623
I WAS MAKING A POINT.

15:22.656 --> 15:25.058
SHE'S TRYING TO MAKE AGRESTIC
A DRUG‐FREE ZONE,

15:25.092 --> 15:28.529
BUT I THINK DRUGS
SHOULD BE LEGAL.

15:29.830 --> 15:31.465
WHY?

15:31.498 --> 15:34.601
BECAUSE.

15:34.635 --> 15:39.039
SO NO ONE GETS IN TROUBLE.

15:42.309 --> 15:46.180
NOBODY'S GONNA GET
IN TROUBLE, OKAY?

15:51.118 --> 15:52.886
BUY YOURSELF A NEW CAR.

15:52.920 --> 15:54.254
AWESOME.

15:54.288 --> 15:56.423
HELP ME GET THESE BAGS
IN THE HOUSE,

15:56.456 --> 15:58.625
AND THEN WE CAN GO
TO THE MOVIES.

15:58.659 --> 16:01.295
REALLY?
WHAT MOVIE?

16:01.328 --> 16:03.463
UH,
HOW ABOUT THE AL GORE ONE

16:03.497 --> 16:06.400
ABOUT THE TOTAL DESTRUCTION
OF THE PLANET

16:06.433 --> 16:09.937
AND THE COMING
ENVIRONMENTAL APOCALYPSE?

16:09.970 --> 16:12.172
COOL.

16:14.074 --> 16:15.843
WHERE'S
MY MICROWAVE POPCORN?

16:15.876 --> 16:18.879
NOW, I KNOW I HAD ONE LEFT
IN HERE.

16:18.912 --> 16:21.114
HEYLIA,
WHERE ARE OUR CUSTOMERS ‐‐

16:21.148 --> 16:25.185
VERNON, KIKI, NANCY,
THAT GUY WITH THE HARELIP?

16:25.219 --> 16:26.286
WE AIN'T BEEN MOVING SHIT.

16:26.320 --> 16:28.388
AND I HEAR THERE'S
A NEW STRAIN OUT THERE

16:28.422 --> 16:30.591
THAT EVERYBODY WANTS,
AND WE AIN'T GOT.

16:30.624 --> 16:32.326
GIRL, IT'S THE ECONOMY.

16:32.359 --> 16:35.362
AND THE
MEDICAL MARIJUANA CLUBS.

16:35.395 --> 16:37.030
YOU KNOW,
I HEARD THEY OPENING UP

16:37.064 --> 16:39.032
ONE OF THEM DRIVE‐THROUGHS
IN THE VALLEY.

16:39.066 --> 16:41.468
NO, HEYLIA.

16:41.502 --> 16:44.671
LOOK AROUND.
WHAT'S MISSING HERE?

16:46.974 --> 16:49.877
MAKE SURE YOU GET ALL THE ASH
OFF OF MY HEEL, TOO.

16:49.910 --> 16:52.379
YO, THIS HERE'S TEENYA.

16:52.412 --> 16:53.180
HI.

16:53.213 --> 16:55.716
SHE'S STUDYING
THAT COSMONOLOGY.

16:55.749 --> 16:57.684
IT'S COSMETOLOGY.

16:57.718 --> 16:59.920
I'LL THROW THIS BEER ON YOU.
SAY SOMETHING ELSE.

16:59.953 --> 17:02.589
SO, LOUIS, TELL ME
ABOUT THAT NEW STRAIN

17:02.623 --> 17:04.024
EVERYBODY BEEN TALKING UP.

17:04.057 --> 17:05.392
I AIN'T LOUIS NO MORE,

17:05.425 --> 17:08.095
AND I AIN'T TELLING YOU SHIT
UNLESS YOU CALL ME U‐TURN.

17:08.128 --> 17:10.330
LOUIS IS A PERFECTLY GOOD NAME,

17:10.364 --> 17:14.535
BUT IF YOU WANT TO BE SOME
TRAFFIC VIOLATION, FINE BY ME.

17:14.568 --> 17:17.437
U‐TURN, WHY THE FUCK
AIN'T I GOT THIS NEW WEED?

17:17.471 --> 17:20.407
NOW, HOW IS IT THAT
MISS HEYLIA JAMES DON'T KNOW?

17:20.440 --> 17:24.244
YOU GETTING SOFT
IN YOUR OLD AGE OR SOMETHING?

17:24.278 --> 17:25.345
[ LAUGHS ]

17:25.379 --> 17:29.349
YOU BETTER MIND YOURSELF,
MR. U‐TURN.

17:29.383 --> 17:33.053
I SEEN YOUR GANGSTER ASS PLAYING
VIOLIN IN YOUR GRANDMAMA'S HOUSE

17:33.086 --> 17:36.390
WITH A POWDER‐BLUE SUIT
AND WIDE‐ASS LAPELS,

17:36.423 --> 17:37.491
SO STOP FRONTING.

17:37.524 --> 17:39.826
HEYLIA, I DON'T FORGET
WHERE I COME FROM,

17:39.860 --> 17:40.827
BUT SOME PEOPLE DO.

17:40.861 --> 17:42.396
GO ON.

17:42.429 --> 17:46.600
THE STRAIN'S CALLED "MILF" ‐‐
MILF WEED.

17:46.633 --> 17:48.035
IT'S THE BRAND OF THE DAY.

17:48.068 --> 17:50.170
EVERYBODY LOVE THAT SHIT,
TOO.

17:50.204 --> 17:51.371
AND IT'S COMING FROM...

17:51.405 --> 17:53.574
OH, MAN,
WHY I GOT TO BE THE ONE

17:53.607 --> 17:55.075
TO TELL YOU THE WAY IT IS?

17:55.108 --> 17:57.411
'CAUSE I STARTED YOU
AND I'LL FINISH YOU

17:57.444 --> 18:00.547
AND I NEED TO HEAR IT,
SO SPEAK THE FUCK UP.

18:00.581 --> 18:02.883
FINE.

18:02.916 --> 18:04.718
IT'S YOUR BOY, CONRAD.

18:04.751 --> 18:06.687
YEAH, HIM
AND A WHITE BITCH ‐‐

18:06.720 --> 18:08.388
THEY GOT THEMSELVES
A REAL GAME.

18:08.422 --> 18:09.089
I GOT TO SAY,
THEY'RE FUCKING GREAT AT IT.

18:09.122 --> 18:10.624
THEY FARMERS NOW.

18:15.562 --> 18:17.865
JUST PUT YOUR HANDS OUT AND SEND
LOVE VIBRATIONS TO THE PLANT.

18:17.898 --> 18:20.334
THAT WAY, THE PERSON WHO SMOKES
IT WILL FEEL THE LOVE, TOO.

18:20.367 --> 18:22.536
I THINK THE PERSON
THAT GREW MY LAST POT SENT

18:22.569 --> 18:26.707
"EAT MINI‐DONUTS WHILE PLAYING
WITH YOUR BALLS" VIBRATIONS.

18:26.740 --> 18:28.809
YOU AIN'T
TAKING ME SERIOUS.

18:28.842 --> 18:32.012
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

18:32.045 --> 18:33.680
THAT SANJAY?

18:39.353 --> 18:42.856
I THINK
IT'S A JEHOVAH'S WITNESS.

18:42.890 --> 18:46.093
WE'RE SHINTO.

18:46.126 --> 18:48.529
EXCUSE ME. HELLO?
HEY, HEY, HEY.

18:48.562 --> 18:49.663
IT'S COOL. IT'S COOL.

18:59.373 --> 19:03.644
HEYLIA,
I CAME TO YOU FIRST.

19:03.677 --> 19:05.045
YOU SHUT ME DOWN.

19:05.078 --> 19:11.418
THERE AIN'T NO EXCUSES
FOR WHAT YOU DONE HERE.

19:11.451 --> 19:13.820
I LAID OUT MY PLANS.
YOU LAUGHED AT ME.

19:13.854 --> 19:17.524
WE DON'T GROW.

19:17.558 --> 19:18.625
WE DEAL.

19:18.659 --> 19:20.894
THAT'S WHAT WE DO.

19:20.928 --> 19:23.463
THAT'S WHAT YOU DO.

19:23.497 --> 19:26.700
I'M A GROWN MAN, HEYLIA, AND
YOU GOT TO SEE ME LIKE THAT.

19:28.635 --> 19:30.938
ALL I SEE

19:30.971 --> 19:34.041
IS THAT YOU WENT OFF
WITH ONE OF MY CUSTOMERS

19:34.074 --> 19:37.678
AND CREATED A NEW GAME
BEHIND MY BACK.

19:37.711 --> 19:40.881
YOU LIED TO ME.

19:40.914 --> 19:44.985
YOU TOOK BUSINESS FROM ME.

19:45.018 --> 19:47.154
THAT AIN'T
HOW A GROWN MAN ACTS.

19:49.957 --> 19:52.860
HEYLIA, I CAN HELP YOU NOW.

19:52.893 --> 19:54.361
YOU COULD RETIRE EARLY.

19:54.394 --> 19:57.297
WE COULD PUT MONEY ASIDE
FOR LeVAN'S EDUCATION.

19:57.331 --> 19:58.866
NO, NO, NO, NO.
UNH‐UNH.

19:58.899 --> 20:02.269
YOU'RE A LITTLE PIGGY.
MM‐HMM.

20:02.302 --> 20:05.272
AND WHAT YOU BUILT HERE,
IT AIN'T RIGHT.

20:05.305 --> 20:09.243
AND SOME DAY, THE BIG BAD WOLF'S
GONNA HUFF AND PUFF

20:09.276 --> 20:11.311
AND BLOW YOUR HOUSE DOWN.

20:11.345 --> 20:14.982
AND WHEN IT HAPPENS, I DON'T
WANT TO BE ANYWHERE NEAR YOU.

20:15.015 --> 20:17.918
YOU AIN'T GOT NO FAITH
IN YOUR BOY.

20:17.951 --> 20:20.454
DIDN'T YOU JUST SAY
YOU WAS A MAN?

20:20.487 --> 20:23.357
NOW, SEE,
YOU CAN'T HAVE IT BOTH WAYS.

20:23.390 --> 20:25.826
YOU AIN'T WELCOME IN MY HOUSE
NO MORE ‐‐

20:25.859 --> 20:29.997
NOT YOU, NOT BARBIE.

20:30.030 --> 20:32.199
I DON'T KNOW YOU.

20:35.802 --> 20:37.638
NOW...

20:37.671 --> 20:42.309
GIVE ME THREE POUNDS
OF THAT FUCKING MILF WEED.

20:42.342 --> 20:45.712
I GOT BUSINESS
TO TAKE CARE OF.

20:58.492 --> 21:01.128
WHY'S IT GOT TO BE LIKE THIS,
HEYLIA?

21:03.263 --> 21:06.533
YOU WANTED TO BE ON YOUR OWN.

21:06.567 --> 21:07.701
YOU ON YOUR OWN.

21:14.842 --> 21:17.644
WHO'S THIS BARBIE GIRL?
IS SHE HOT?

21:21.715 --> 21:26.887
IF YOU WILL NOTICE ABOVE ME,
OUR VERY FIRST CAMERA.

21:26.920 --> 21:30.090
AND BELOW IT,
OUR "DRUG FREE ZONE" SIGN.

21:30.123 --> 21:32.092
WE'RE LETTING THESE PUSHERS KNOW

21:32.125 --> 21:34.461
WE ARE KEEPING
AN EYE ON THEM.

21:34.494 --> 21:38.966
AGRESTIC IS NOW OFFICIALLY
A DRUG‐FREE ZONE.

21:38.999 --> 21:40.901
[ METAL CLANGS ]
DOUCHEBAG!

21:40.934 --> 21:42.469
WHAT THE FUCK?

21:42.503 --> 21:44.471
BITCH!
GO HOME!

21:44.505 --> 21:45.639
YOU HATE DOGS!

21:45.672 --> 21:48.075
CRAZY DOG FREAKS!

21:48.108 --> 21:52.379
I AM PROTECTING
THE HUMANS OF AGRESTIC.

21:52.412 --> 21:56.583
NOW, OUR CAMERAS
WILL BE RUNNING 24/7.

21:56.617 --> 21:58.852
GIVE US BACK
OUR DOG PARK.

21:58.886 --> 22:00.087
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

22:00.120 --> 22:02.523
WELL, I CAN SEE ALL THE CRAZIES
ARE OUT TODAY.

22:02.556 --> 22:05.659
IS IT TRUE YOU HAVE A DRINKING
PROBLEM, COUNCILWOMAN HODES?

22:10.230 --> 22:12.132
Silas: NANCY HAS
NO IDEA WHO I AM.

22:12.165 --> 22:14.301
SUCKS TO NEVER BE SEEN,
NEVER APPRECIATED.

22:14.334 --> 22:18.138
SUCKS WHEN THE PIE GETS EATEN
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU,

22:18.172 --> 22:20.641
AND YOU HELPED BAKE
THAT PIE.

22:20.674 --> 22:21.508
WHAT PIE?

22:21.542 --> 22:23.677
IT'S A METAPHORICAL PIE.

22:23.710 --> 22:25.612
AM I EATING THE PIE?

22:25.646 --> 22:26.413
SORT OF.

22:26.446 --> 22:27.748
YOU'RE BENEFITING
FROM THAT PIE.

22:27.781 --> 22:30.884
BUT, REALLY, NO. NO PIE FOR YOU
EITHER, MY YOUNG FRIEND.

22:30.918 --> 22:32.019
[ SIGHS ]

22:32.052 --> 22:34.688
WHERE'S OUR FUCKING PIE?

22:34.721 --> 22:36.156
LIFE SUCKS.

22:36.190 --> 22:39.493
COME ON, NOW.
LIFE DOES NOT SUCK...

22:39.526 --> 22:43.497
UNLESS YOU HAVE NO JOB,
NO GIRLFRIEND,

22:43.530 --> 22:44.798
EIGHT TOES.

22:44.831 --> 22:46.533
[ SCOFFS ]

22:46.567 --> 22:47.901
LIFE SUCKS.

22:47.935 --> 22:49.570
ANYWAY,
YOUR MOM KNOWS NOTHING

22:49.603 --> 22:52.039
ABOUT WHAT IT TAKES
TO BE A CRIME LORD.

22:52.072 --> 22:54.608
I UNDERSTAND BUSINESS.
I AM AN ENTREPRENEUR.

22:54.641 --> 22:56.343
I WOULD BE GREAT AT IT.

22:56.376 --> 23:00.380
I MEAN, I MAY NOT BE SOME
BRAINIAC, BUT I KNOW WEED.

23:00.414 --> 23:02.783
IT'S THE FAMILY BUSINESS,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

23:02.816 --> 23:05.552
I SAY FORGET HER.

23:05.586 --> 23:07.154
WE START OUR OWN BUSINESS.

23:07.187 --> 23:10.190
EXCEPT WE HAVE NO MONEY.

23:11.692 --> 23:12.659
YEAH.

23:15.329 --> 23:16.663
WAS SHE IMPRESSED?
COULD YOU TELL?

23:16.697 --> 23:17.998
WHAT DID SHE THINK
OF OUR PLACE?

23:18.031 --> 23:20.067
SHE NEVER WANTS
TO SEE US AGAIN, NANCY.

23:20.100 --> 23:21.368
SHE WAS STONE COLD.

23:21.401 --> 23:23.804
BUT, LIKE, ACTING COLD
BECAUSE SHE WAS SECRETLY DAZZLED

23:23.837 --> 23:25.005
BY HOW WELL WE'VE DONE?

23:25.038 --> 23:27.174
WHAT,
YOU NEED HEYLIA'S APPROVAL?

23:27.207 --> 23:29.209
SHE BOUGHT THREE POUNDS.
OF THE MILF?

23:29.243 --> 23:33.146
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE SO PROUD
OF THE NAME, OKAY?
OKAY.

23:33.180 --> 23:34.848
WHY DID SHE BUY FROM US?

23:34.882 --> 23:36.416
SO THAT SHE CAN SELL IT
TO OTHERS.

23:36.450 --> 23:38.418
THAT'S WHAT SHE DOES
FOR A LIVING.

23:38.452 --> 23:40.387
ALL HER CUSTOMERS
ARE ASKING FOR OUR SHIT.

23:40.420 --> 23:42.422
YOU CAN'T SELL
WHAT YOU DON'T HAVE.

23:42.456 --> 23:44.892
THAT'S KIND OF AWESOME.
NO, IT AIN'T.

23:44.925 --> 23:46.994
YES, IT IS.

23:47.027 --> 23:48.262
SHE BOUGHT OUR STUFF,

23:48.295 --> 23:50.531
AND SHE'LL BUY MORE
'CAUSE IT'S GOOD.

23:50.564 --> 23:52.432
SHE'S NOT GONNA STAY MAD.

23:52.466 --> 23:54.034
SHE CAN'T.

23:54.067 --> 23:56.470
WOMAN,
YOU DO NOT KNOW HEYLIA.

23:56.503 --> 23:58.305
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

24:00.340 --> 24:02.242
HI, SHANE.

24:03.844 --> 24:06.446
I CAME TO PICK UP YOUR MOM.

24:06.480 --> 24:09.683
SHE'S DOING LAUNDRY
WITH SOME BLACK GUY.

24:10.884 --> 24:14.521
WOULD YOU TELL HER
THAT I'M HERE, PLEASE?

24:16.223 --> 24:18.859
WHAT'S CONRAD DOING
AT YOUR HOUSE?

24:18.892 --> 24:21.495
NOT A GREAT IDEA,
BY THE WAY.

24:21.528 --> 24:25.432
JUST SOME OLD BUSINESS WITH
HEYLIA HE WANTED TO TALK ABOUT.

24:25.465 --> 24:26.366
HEYLIA JAMES?

24:26.400 --> 24:28.268
YOU'RE NOT GONNA HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT HER.

24:28.302 --> 24:29.837
WHAT?
SHE'S BEING TAKEN CARE OF.

24:29.870 --> 24:32.472
NO.

24:32.506 --> 24:34.441
WE DON'T NEED THAT.

24:34.474 --> 24:38.145
THERE'S REALLY NO PROBLEM
WITH HEYLIA, REALLY.

24:38.178 --> 24:41.281
WELL, NOW THAT'S GUARANTEED.

24:41.315 --> 24:45.285
I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU DIDN'T CARE ABOUT POT,

24:45.319 --> 24:47.321
THAT WE WERE
UNDER YOUR RADAR.

24:47.354 --> 24:49.289
NO, BABE.
YOU'RE UNDER MY RADAR.

24:49.323 --> 24:51.058
AND SINCE
I'M KEEPING YOU THERE,

24:51.091 --> 24:52.960
I GOT TO SHOW MY BOSS
SOME RESULTS.

24:52.993 --> 24:56.196
WHY DON'T YOU SHOW HIM
SOME OTHER RESULTS

24:56.230 --> 24:59.399
LIKE A CRACK DEN
OR A METH LAB OR SOMETHING?

24:59.433 --> 25:02.269
HEYLIA'S GONNA LEAD ME
TO THIS GUY NAMED U‐TURN

25:02.302 --> 25:05.138
WHO'S DEALING A LOT MORE
THAN WEED.

25:05.172 --> 25:08.475
WELL, WHY NOT ARREST HIM
AND KEEP HEYLIA OUT OF IT?

25:08.509 --> 25:12.513
SWEETIE, YOU GOT TO DIG THE
WORMS TO CATCH THE BIG FISH.

25:12.546 --> 25:13.514
HEYLIA'S BEING DUG UP,

25:13.547 --> 25:15.349
AND I DON'T WANT TO TALK
ABOUT THIS ANYMORE.

25:16.750 --> 25:19.620
THIS IS MY FUN TIME.

25:23.991 --> 25:27.361
I'M THINKING TAPAS.
YOU UP FOR IT?

25:39.006 --> 25:42.276
♪♪ GOT A NEW REVELATION ♪♪

25:42.309 --> 25:46.847
♪♪ RIGHT ON THE WALL ♪♪

25:46.880 --> 25:51.652
♪♪ YEAH,
I GOT A NEW INSPIRATION ♪♪

